{"tid":1484563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"後日同佢地遍地開花。但今晚大家散。","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:10:42.000Z","uid":195252,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e227b343d027fb1b247e78a46354d48c5d02c3","tid":1484563,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"政府發左聲明回應今日集會<br />\n<br />\n內容如下<br />\n<br />\n政府就維園集會作出回應<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　政府發言人今日（八月十八日）回應在維多利亞公園舉辦的公眾集會時表示，雖然集會期間大致和平，但由於參與者佔用了港島多條主要幹道，路面交通大受影響，對市民造成不便。運輸署與警方已積極協調，盡量將影響減至最少。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　發言人重申，目前最重要的是要盡快回復社會秩序；當一切平靜之後，政府會與市民展開真誠對話，致力修補撕裂，重建社會和諧。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月18日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時18分<br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n<br />\n個人認為需要行動升級。<br />\n呢方面大家可以討論<br />\n但今晚大家真係要散，擇日再戰。"},{"pid":"a6ae2de605759331b99162d7c57928cf8d3beda6","tid":1484563,"uid":186845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"走啦 唔好留"},{"pid":"fd79147e177a85bba3f3f5e043875d29f466af00","tid":1484563,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位要<strong>行</strong>落金鐘叫人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n仆街，依家好關鍵！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1484298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1484298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f53326db731cce86cc203aea7f1bafb8b2c587b7","tid":1484563,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:23.000Z","msg":"點解係後日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b34a916fd5761e1e67af06cc0b4a2f00431555","tid":1484563,"uid":195252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f53326db731cce86cc203aea7f1bafb8b2c587b7","tid":1484563,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:23.000Z","msg":"點